Although this file is a usable description of the base protocol,
when extensions are to supported, it may be desirable to divide into
multiple files.
The following script can be used for that purpose:


<CODE BEGINS>

#!/usr/local/bin/perl
open(IN,"rpcrdma-v2.x");
open(OUT,">temp.x");
while(<IN>)
{
  if (m/FILE ENDS: (.*)$/)
    {
      close(OUT);
      rename("temp.x", $1);
      open(OUT,">temp.x");
    }
    else
    {
      print OUT $_;
    }
}
close(IN);
close(OUT);

<CODE ENDS>
